HEADWORD: Zoroaster
<hw>Zo`ro*as"ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>The Persian
prophet <altname>Zarathustra</altname>, who probably lived in the second
millennium B. C. His teachings form the basis for the religion
Zoroastrianism.</def>⟦br⟧
